window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A cultivation progression epic.</p> <p>Ages ago, the world was filled with mythical beasts and cultivators who could shake the heavens. Legends say they still exist and want to return home, but an enemy has blocked the path.</p> <p>Trapped among the stars, a father's desire to send his son to safety collides with destiny.</p> <p>The son's name is Verse.</p> <p>After passing through the River of Fate, his memories are scrambled with those of others, including a soldier and a cultivator from a heavenly sect, but he survives.</p> <p>First, he'll have to find the strength to survive in a world where cultivation is the only law.</p> <p>Then he's going to find out what happened.</p> <p>In this story, you can expect <i>xianxia</i>-style immortal cultivation, reincarnation, a focus on jade and sunset magic, sects, alchemy, formations, ancient races, and a hero who is born from one of them.</p>"; 
